title: Help a fellow League Player!

embed.description: I prank call Bob Francis from Adelaide talkback radio station 5aa. Bob is infamous for getting angry and abusive with people he doesn't agree with or prank c...

body:
Hey guys.   Funny prank calls to radio stations. Please help a brudda out and follow the link give me some views and likes. They are only short videos

If you have a channel then leave me a comment on one of my videos and I will return the favour. Good karma!

replies.body:
The last time you posted this it got downvoted to Hell for a reason. I will consider watching something else you make if you post it, in the hopes you might actually be able to make something decent.
However, I don't want a channel full of this crap to be clogging up YouTube. The only fans you will get are not the fans you should want. One day, when you have grown up, you will realise how immature stuff like this is.

Please just stop posting this on the forums.

http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/miscellaneous/8EMfB3xp-please-view-and-give-me-feedback

same post downvoted already.

it's a real pity that you havent gotten the *message* yet.
